  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHECK OUT OUR UPCOMING GAME</h2></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Run Prop, Run!</h2><i>Run Prop, Run!</i> is a <strong>multiplayer hide'n'seek</strong> game. It is inspired by the classic Prop Hunt mod where players must disguise themselves as an object in the scenery to avoid detection by a hunter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/c4963a482b80b11f608ae2efc4bca180.poster.avif?t=1758830078\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/c4963a482b80b11f608ae2efc4bca180.webm?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/c4963a482b80b11f608ae2efc4bca180.mp4?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Run Prop, Run!</i> can have up to 12 players and begins with one <strong>Hunter</strong> trying to catch other hiding <strong>Prop</strong> players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/409ed4a11dd297b46f7d83e9854c98d4.poster.avif?t=1758830078\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/409ed4a11dd297b46f7d83e9854c98d4.webm?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/409ed4a11dd297b46f7d83e9854c98d4.mp4?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As each <strong>Prop</strong> gets caught, they will turn into Hunters making it more and more difficult for the remaining <strong>Props</strong> to survive the hunt.<br>To help the <strong>Props</strong> survive, they are given the ability to transform into any object in the stage so they can better blend into the environment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/67046684016ddbf4e31cd7255b7b385b.poster.avif?t=1758830078\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/67046684016ddbf4e31cd7255b7b385b.webm?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/67046684016ddbf4e31cd7255b7b385b.mp4?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>When a Hunter captures a prop, it turns it into a Hunter. Start 1 Hunter VS 11 Props, and finish with up to 11 Hunters VS 1 prop!</i><br><i>It's not just Prop Hunt Hide and Seek. There's a lot of mechanics revolving around platforming, abilities, and strategy!</i><br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHECK OUT OUR UPCOMING GAME</h2></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Run Prop, Run!</h2><i>Run Prop, Run!</i> is a <strong>multiplayer hide'n'seek</strong> game. It is inspired by the classic Prop Hunt mod where players must disguise themselves as an object in the scenery to avoid detection by a hunter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/c4963a482b80b11f608ae2efc4bca180.poster.avif?t=1758830078\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/c4963a482b80b11f608ae2efc4bca180.webm?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/c4963a482b80b11f608ae2efc4bca180.mp4?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Run Prop, Run!</i> can have up to 12 players and begins with one <strong>Hunter</strong> trying to catch other hiding <strong>Prop</strong> players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/409ed4a11dd297b46f7d83e9854c98d4.poster.avif?t=1758830078\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/409ed4a11dd297b46f7d83e9854c98d4.webm?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/409ed4a11dd297b46f7d83e9854c98d4.mp4?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As each <strong>Prop</strong> gets caught, they will turn into Hunters making it more and more difficult for the remaining <strong>Props</strong> to survive the hunt.<br>To help the <strong>Props</strong> survive, they are given the ability to transform into any object in the stage so they can better blend into the environment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/67046684016ddbf4e31cd7255b7b385b.poster.avif?t=1758830078\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/67046684016ddbf4e31cd7255b7b385b.webm?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475400/extras/67046684016ddbf4e31cd7255b7b385b.mp4?t=1758830078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>When a Hunter captures a prop, it turns it into a Hunter. Start 1 Hunter VS 11 Props, and finish with up to 11 Hunters VS 1 prop!</i><br><i>It's not just Prop Hunt Hide and Seek. There's a lot of mechanics revolving around platforming, abilities, and strategy!</i><br><br>",
